reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Tasty gummies that make you feel good, even if they take a bit to get used to
reviews.reviewText: I've been taking SmartyPants Men's Formula gummy multivitamins for a few months now, and I'm really liking them. They taste a bit strange at first, but you quickly get used to them. And I'm not sure if it's the vitamins or just a placebo effect, but I feel better overall since I started taking them. I have more energy, and I haven't been sick at all.If you're looking for a gummy multivitamin that's easy to take and made with good ingredients, I recommend SmartyPants. Just be prepared for a bit of a weird taste at first.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars OMG these are delicious
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. When I first saw the instructions said to take 4 per day, I thought “man that’s a lot,” but I’m so glad it’s not less than that because I could eat 20 of these things. They’re so delicious.The ingredients are fantastic and I really like the messages on the packaging, such as every batch being third-party lab tested, everything is organic, it’s probiotic, did I mention delicious? The texture is *similar* to a gummy (in that yes, it’s squishy), but not exactly. Your teeth bite straight through with very little pressure. I actually love it. They’re much more quick to dissolve than a traditional gummy and way easier to chew. If you ask me, they’re just straight up awesome.Update - FYI: Don’t buy these if they’re on sale. I did, and got a batch that was loaded with moisture. Tossed them out. These gummies are supposed to be completely dry so a good batch will have no moisture inside and the gummies will feel dry to the touch. No stickiness at all.
